Symbol.Script_3D:
!! Round Gable Louver.gsm
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end
if gs_shadow=1 then SHADOW ON if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
alpha=360/gs_resol
ADDx a/2 rotx 90 addy a/2
!!Frame!!
pen gs_cont_pen material fmat
r=a/2
!For additional 2 points coordinate in base polyline !to solve smooth surface problems gamma=atn((5/16")/(fth*2/8)) delta=atn((fth*1/16)/(1 9/16"))
alpha=-alpha for i=1 to gs_resol+3 step 1 put r*cos(alpha),r*sin(alpha),0 alpha=alpha+360/gs_resol next i
ee=0.00001 !"small" value
!! Model Solid tubea 11,nsp/3,0, 0,0,0, 2 1/2",0,0,
2 1/2",fth*11/16-ee,1, 2 1/2",fth*11/16,0, 2 1/2"-ee*cos(delta),fth*11/16+ee*sin(delta),1,
15/16"+ee*cos(delta),fth*12/16-ee*sin(delta),1, 15/16",fth*12/16,0, 15/16"-ee*sin(gamma),fth*12/16+ee*cos(gamma),1,
5/8",fth,0, 0,fth,0, 0,0,0,
get (nsp)
body -1
!!Louvers!!
pen gs_cont_pen material lmat
! Cut Plane angle calculation
alpha=360/gs_resol dev=(a/2-2.5")-(a/2-2.5")*cos(alpha/2)
rotz alpha/2 for i=1 to gs_resol step 1 addx a/2-2.5"-dev cutplane 0,1,1,0 del 1 rotz alpha next i del gs_resol+1
n=int(a/lw)+1
add a/2,-lw/2,0 roty -90
for i=1 to int(n/2) step 1 prism_ 7,a, !!!0,0,15, fth*5/8,0,15, fth*5/8,lw*2/7,15, fth*1/8,lw,15, 0,lw,15, 0,lw*5/7,15, fth*4/8,0,15, fth*5/8,0,-1 !!!0,0,-1
base vert 0,0,0 vert 0,0,-1 vert 0,1,0 vert 1,0,0 coor 2,-1,-2,-3,-4 body 1 addy lw next i del int(n/2)
addy -lw for i=1 to int(n/2)-1 step 1 prism_ 7,a, !!0,0,15, fth*5/8,0,15, fth*5/8,lw*2/7,15, fth*1/8,lw,15, 0,lw,15, 0,lw*5/7,15, fth*4/8,0,15, fth*5/8,0,-1 !!0,0,-1
base vert 0,0,0 vert 0,0,-1 vert 0,1,0 vert 1,0,0 coor 2,-1,-2,-3,-4 body 1 addy -lw next i del int(n/2)+2
for i=1 to gs_resol step 1 cutend next i
del 3
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Round Gable Louver.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen ADD2 a/2,0 fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 1+2+64,gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2,-fth,0, a/2,-fth,0, a/2,0,0, -a/2,0,0, -a/2,-fth,-1
rect2 -a/2,0,a/2,-fth
hotspot2 -a/2,0 hotspot2 0,0 hotspot2 0,-fth/2 hotspot2 -a/2,-fth hotspot2 a/2,-fth hotspot2 a/2,0 end
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
parameters b=fth lock "b"
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=2 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
if gs_resol<3 then parameters gs_resol=3
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
